  "title": "Tech Support/Admin",
  "description": "<p>As a Project and Operations Administrative support of our team, this role is crucial in supporting the Project Managers to maintain effective and efficient application system operations and monitoring across our organization.</p>\n<p>The successful candidate will work with cross-functional teams to provide value-added support to make a significant impact on our organization's technology projects and operations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Liaison for Project Manager for augmented resources/interns periodical administration (requisition, timesheet tracking, reflection reports, leave application, etc)</li>\n  <li>Support Project Managers to hire and onboard / offboard project team members,  Security Clearance, Onboarding/offboarding checklist.</li>\n  <li>Assists Project Managers in term of project administration activities such as financials tracker and augmented resources renewal tracker.</li>\n  <li>Support Project Managers in Project and Operation Documentations and tracking (including pre-audit preparations for audits).</li>\n  <li>Track account and vulnerability compliance status, and incident tracking. Prepare operational statistics, server utilization,n and performance metrics for weekly operations meetings to comply with key risk indicators for<br>\nrunning projects and operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What are we looking for:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A degree in business management, business administration or a related field.</li>\n  <li>5+ years of experience as a Project Admin/ PMO or related project administrative role, preferably in IT or relevant industries.</li>\n  <li>Meticulous with an eye for detail.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and assume responsibility for project deliverables.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of organizational effectiveness and operations management.</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Excellent organizational skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency with Microsoft Office (Words, Excel, PowerPoint, etc)</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal, team player, meticulous, analytical, and writing skills</li>\n</ul>",
